## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5b483-102">宣告是由簽發者的主體相關的陳述式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-102">A claim is a statement about a subject by an issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-103">宣告表示的主旨可用於驗證和授權的作業內容的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-103">Claims represent attributes of the subject that are useful in the context of authentication and authorization operations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-104">主旨和簽發者是這兩個實體的身分識別案例的一部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-104">Subjects and issuers are both entities that are part of an identity scenario.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-105">主體的一些常見的範例： 使用者、 應用程式或服務、 裝置或電腦。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-105">Some typical examples of a subject are: a user, an application or service, a device, or a computer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-106">簽發者的一些常見的範例： 作業系統、 應用程式、 服務、 角色提供者、 身分識別提供者或同盟提供者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-106">Some typical examples of an issuer are: the operating system, an application, a service, a role provider, an identity provider, or a federation provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-107">簽發者傳遞宣告發行安全性權杖，通常是透過安全性權杖服務 (STS)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-107">An issuer delivers claims by issuing security tokens, typically through a Security Token Service (STS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-108">(在 WIF 中，您可以建置的 STS，藉由衍生自<xref:System.IdentityModel.SecurityTokenService>類別。)在某些情況下，可以延伸主體屬性儲存在資源上直接收到來自簽發者的宣告集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-108">(In WIF, you can build an STS by deriving from the <xref:System.IdentityModel.SecurityTokenService> class.) On occasion, the collection of claims received from an issuer can be extended by subject attributes stored directly at the resource.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-109">宣告可以評估以判斷資料的存取權限及其他受保護資源的授權程序期間，並也可用來進行，或有關主旨 express 驗證決策。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-109">A claim can be evaluated to determine access rights to data and other secured resources during the process of authorization and can also be used to make or express authentication decisions about a subject.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5b483-110">從.NET 4.5 開始，Windows Identity Foundation (WIF) 類別，實作宣告式身分識別，已完全整合至.NET Framework。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-110">Beginning with .NET 4.5, the Windows Identity Foundation (WIF) classes, which implement claims-based identity, have been fully integrated into the .NET Framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-111">宣告的概念由實作<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-111">The claims concept is implemented by the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5b483-112">下列程式碼說明的重要屬性<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim>類別：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-112">The following describes important properties of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim> class:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5b483-113"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A>屬性是包含宣告的語意資訊的字串 (通常是 URI)，它會告訴您宣告值的表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-113">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A> property is a string (typically a URI) that contains the semantic information about the claim; it tells you what the value of the claim means.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-114">例如，宣告類型的宣告<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes.GivenName>(「http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity/claims/givenname") 代表使用者的名字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-114">For example, a claim with a claim type of <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes.GivenName> ("http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2005/05/identity/claims/givenname") represents a user's first name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-115">值<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A>屬性可以是其中一項中定義的已知宣告類型<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes>類別或它可以是任意的 URI 所定義的簽發者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-115">The value of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Type%2A> property can be one of the well-known claim types defined in the <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimTypes> class, or it can be an arbitrary URI as defined by the issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-116">例如，"urn: spendinglimit"的宣告類型可能代表其合理的商務內容中的簽發者的使用者屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-116">For example, a claim type of "urn:spendinglimit" might represent a user attribute which makes sense within the business context of the issuer.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5b483-117"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A>屬性包含宣告的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-117">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A> property contains the value of the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-118">若要降低相依性，並簡化管理，在 WIF 中的宣告的值是僅以字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-118">In order to reduce dependencies and simplify administration, in WIF the value of a claim is represented only as a string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-119">對於更複雜的數值類型，建議您使用標準的 XML 結構描述類型，以指出值如何是要序列化，以及從字串還原序列化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-119">For more complex value types, it is recommended that you use standard XML schema types to indicate how the value is meant to be serialized into and deserialized from a string.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5b483-120"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A>屬性包含識別值的型別資訊的字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-120">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A> property contains a string that identifies the type information for the value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-121">若要了解值的格式，並提供有關如何將它還原序列化的資訊，則應該使用這個屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-121">This property should be used to understand the format of the value and to provide information about how to deserialize it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-122">如果您的解決方案需要複雜的實值型別，建議您使用中的標準 XML 結構描述型別<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A>屬性，指出如何<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A>屬性是用來序列化，從字串還原序列化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-122">If your solution requires complex value types, it is recommended that you use standard XML schema types in the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.ValueType%2A> property to indicate how the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Value%2A> property is meant to be serialized into and deserialized from a string.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5b483-123"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Subject%2A>屬性是<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity>物件，表示宣告主體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-123">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Subject%2A> property is a <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity> object that represents the subject of the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-124">宣告主體相關宣告會判斷提示是實體 （通常要求資源的存取權的使用者）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-124">The subject of the claim is the entity (typically the user who is requesting access to a resource) about which the claim is asserted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-125"><xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity>包含，其屬性之間的描述屬性的宣告集合和屬性主體，以證明的一或多個簽發者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-125">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsIdentity> contains, among its properties, a collection of claims that describe the properties and attributes of the subject as attested to by one or more issuers.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5b483-126"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A>屬性包含發出宣告之實體的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-126">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A> property contains the name of the entity that issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-127">宣告簽發者是在 WIF 中以包含取自簽發者名稱登錄會維護一份已知的簽發者名稱的字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-127">The issuer of a claim is represented in WIF by a string that contains a name taken from a list of well-known issuers that is maintained by the issuer name registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-128">簽發者名稱登錄是衍生自類別的執行個體<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-128">The issuer name registry is an instance of a class that derives from the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.IssuerNameRegistry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-129">簽發者名稱登錄的名稱相關聯助憶鍵來驗證對應簽發者所產生之權杖的簽章所需的加密編譯內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-129">The issuer name registry associates a mnemonic name to the cryptographic material needed to verify the signatures of tokens produced by the corresponding issuer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-130">比方說， <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> .NET 4.5 中，現成可用類別會將每個簽發者的助憶鍵名稱關聯其相對應的 X.509 憑證。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-130">For example, the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> class, available out of the box with .NET 4.5, associates the mnemonic name for each issuer with its corresponding X.509 certificate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-131">簽發者名稱登錄的已知的簽發者清單通常內建在啟動時。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-131">The list of well-known issuers is typically built at startup time by the issuer name registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-132">所使用的清單<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry>應用程式組態檔中指定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-132">The list used by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.ConfigurationBasedIssuerNameRegistry> is specified in the application configuration file.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5b483-133"><xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A>屬性包含最初發出宣告之實體的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-133">The <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A> property contains the name of the entity that originally issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-134">這個屬性被設計為 dbtype_iunknown，宣告可能通過多個簽發者之前所要的 RP 應用程式的用戶端同盟案例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-134">This property is designed to facilitate scenarios where a claim may pass through multiple issuers before it is presented by the client to the RP application; such as federation scenarios.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-135">您可以檢查<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A>屬性來判斷最初發出宣告的實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-135">You can examine the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.OriginalIssuer%2A> property to determine the entity that originally issued the claim.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-136">名稱已從清單中的已知的簽發者簽發者名稱登錄，如同由維護<xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-136">The name is taken from the list of well-known issuers maintained by the issuer name registry, as in the case of the <xref:System.Security.Claims.Claim.Issuer%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="5b483-137">下列範例會擷取已驗證的使用者執行 HTTP 要求相關聯的宣告，並將其寫入 HTTP 回應中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-137">The following example extracts the claims associated to the authenticated user performing an HTTP request and writes them in the HTTP response.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-138">目前的使用者讀取<xref:System.Web.HttpContext>做為<xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsPrincipal>並從中讀取的宣告。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-138">The current user is read from the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> as a <xref:System.Security.Claims.ClaimsPrincipal> and the claims are read from it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5b483-139">宣告接著會寫入到<xref:System.Web.HttpResponse>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b483-139">The claims are then written to the <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse> object.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
ClaimsPrincipal principal = HttpContext.Current.User as ClaimsPrincipal;  
if (null != principal)  
{  
   foreach (Claim claim in principal.Claims)  
   {  
      Response.Write("CLAIM TYPE: " + claim.Type + "; CLAIM VALUE: " + claim.Value + "</br>");  
   }  
  
}  
  
```
